The issue you're facing is likely due to incorrect handling of Ethereum unit conversions (wei  ether) and possibly miscalculating transaction fees or block rewards. Here's how to fix it:

1. Correct Unit Conversion
EVM chains use wei (1 ether = 10 wei). Your current code is likely treating values as ether instead of wei.
Use web3.utils to convert between units:

